### Demand
- *Demand* - how much of something people are willing or able to buy under certain circumstances.
- Different people by their cell phones at different prices; individual choices summed up form the *market demand*.
- Amount of good that buyers in the market purchase at a specific moment is the *quantity demanded*.
- *Law of Demand*: The lower the price goes, the higher the quantity demanded.



